Privacy Policy

Effective Date: 29 June 2026

Thank you for using Okoro(“the App”). Your privacy is important to us. This Privacy Policy explains what information we collect, how we use it, and the choices you have regarding your information.

Information We Collect

Okoro is designed to minimise the collection of personal information.

Depending on the features you choose to use, the App may collect:

* Location Information – Used to calculate accurate astronomical data such as sunrise, sunset, moonrise, moonset, celestial positions, weather, and tides. Your location is used only with your permission.
* Device Information – Anonymous technical information such as device type, operating system version, and crash reports may be collected to improve the performance and reliability of the App.
* Account Information – If you choose to create an account or subscribe to premium services, we may collect your email address and information necessary to manage your account and purchases.
* Usage Information – Anonymous analytics may be used to understand how features are used and to improve the user experience.

How We Use Your Information

Information collected is used solely to:

* Provide accurate environmental and astronomical information.
* Personalise the App based on your preferences.
* Process subscriptions and in-app purchases.
* Improve app performance and stability.
* Respond to customer support requests.

We do not sell your personal information to third parties.

Location Services

Location access is optional. If granted, your location is used only to calculate accurate local environmental information. You may disable location access at any time through your device settings, although some features may become unavailable or less accurate.

Analytics and Diagnostics

We may use trusted third-party analytics and crash reporting services to help improve the App. These services receive only anonymous or pseudonymous technical information and do not identify you personally.

In-App Purchases

Purchases are securely processed by Apple through the App Store. We do not receive or store your payment card information.

Data Security

We take reasonable technical and organisational measures to protect your information from unauthorised access, loss, misuse, or disclosure.

Data Retention

Personal information is retained only for as long as necessary to provide the services you request, comply with legal obligations, resolve disputes, and enforce our agreements.

Your Rights

Depending on your location, you may have the right to:

* Access the personal information we hold about you.
* Request correction of inaccurate information.
* Request deletion of your personal information.
* Withdraw consent for optional data collection.
* Request a copy of your personal data where applicable.

Requests can be made using the contact details below.

Children’s Privacy

Ōkoro is not intended to knowingly collect personal information from children without appropriate parental consent. If you believe a child has provided personal information, please contact us so it can be removed.

Third-Party Services

The App may integrate with services such as Apple Weather, Apple Maps, Apple Sign In, iCloud, or other Apple frameworks where applicable. These services are governed by their own privacy policies.

Changes to This Policy

We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be published within the App or on our website, together with an updated effective date.

